name: Yeti Rambler 14 Mug
description: Camp coffee will never be the same. Yeti’s Rambler 14 is totally over-engineered for your hydration and caffeination needs. Made of 18/8 stainless steel, it offers that famous Yeti durability plus all the innovation of the Rambler drinkware series: double-wall vacuum insulation, No Sweat design and all the hot/cold temperature boosting you can handle.Durable 18/8 kitchen-grade stainless steel is puncture- and rust-resistant.Double-wall vacuum insulation keeps hot drinks hot and cold drinks cold for hours.Crystal-clear lid (10.2cm opening) helps you gauge whether it's time for a refill.Full-loop welded steel handle withstands abuse.Dishwasher safe for easy cleanup when you're back from your adventure.
